  "title": "NEW! Human Resource Operations Executive *Entry Level*",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide operational and administrative support across HR, Learning & Development, and talent programs, including training coordination, scheduling, tracking, reporting, and documentation.</li><li>Support internship and early-talent programs end-to-end, coordinating job postings, interview logistics, onboarding activities, and program administration.</li><li>Contribute to employee experience and engagement initiatives, assisting with internal events, communications, and maintenance of employee-facing materials, SharePoint sites, and HR system user guides.</li><li>Deliver general HR operations and project support, including invoice and purchase order tracking, data consolidation, report preparation, system testing, and ad-hoc project coordination.</li></ul><p><u>Requirements</u><br /></p><ul><li>At least 1 year of prior experience in HR Operations </li></ul><p>Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Word format and attention it to Rachel Yeo (R22104385).<br />Shortlisted candidates will be notified<br />Data provided is for recruitment purposes only<br />www.ambition.com.sg<br />EA Registration Number: R22104385<br />Business Registration Number: 200611680D. License Number: 10C5117</p>",
